---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Products | SoundIn';
const description = 'Holocron is live and in production with paying customers. Compliance-first venue management for UK nightlife operators.';

const collectionSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'CollectionPage',
  '@id': 'https://soundin.scot/ecosystem#webpage',
  name: title,
  description,
  url: 'https://soundin.scot/ecosystem',
  isPartOf: { '@id': 'https://soundin.scot/#organization' },
};
---

<Layout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical="https://soundin.scot/ecosystem"
  current="ecosystem"
  skipLink={{ href: '#ecosystem-content', label: 'Skip to products' }}
>
  <script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(collectionSchema)} slot="head" />

  <div class="page-hero" id="ecosystem-content" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <span class="page-hero-kicker">products</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">Our products</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="eco-body">
    <div class="eco-intro">
      <p>Holocron is built in two layers. The Compliance Layer ensures you meet legal requirements—attendance records, incident logs, staff procedures—without extra work. The Intelligence Layer surfaces calibrated patterns from your data: when you peak, where incidents cluster, what actually drives revenue. Both layers work from the same record. Free tier for artists, promoters, and security means your entire scene participates.</p>
    </div>

    <article class="holocron" id="holocron">
      <div class="holocron-head">
        <h2 class="holocron-name">Holocron</h2>
        <span class="holocron-badge">Live</span>
      </div>
      <p class="holocron-tagline">
        For venues under 300 capacity across Scotland.
      </p>
      <p class="holocron-desc">
        Venues run on clickers, notebooks, WhatsApp threads, and spreadsheets. Holocron consolidates attendance, incidents, guest lists, ticketing, and settlements into one record. Artists know if their advance is final. Security logs feed directly into compliance records. Settlements are visible to both sides instantly. No fragmentation. No reinterpretation.
      </p>
      <ul class="holocron-features">
        <li>Attendance verified in real time</li>
        <li>Incident logs auto-feed compliance records</li>
        <li>Shared booking &amp; settlement pipeline</li>
        <li>Calibrated guidance after 10 events</li>
        <li>Free access for artists &amp; promoters</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="holocron-traction">
        Live and in production. Venue count coming soon.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://holocron.scot"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="holocron-link"
      >
        Visit holocron.scot <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </article>

    <div class="eco-pipeline">
      <h2 class="eco-pipeline-title">What&rsquo;s next</h2>
      <p class="eco-pipeline-body">
        Phase 2 brings People Pro — deeper intelligence for artists and promoters using that scene graph. One product ships at a time. Announcements go to the newsletter first.
      </p>
      <a href="/newsletter" class="cta-button">Subscribe <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .eco-body {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 64px 120px;
  }

  .eco-intro {
    padding-bottom: 72px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-ghost);
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .eco-intro p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .holocron {
    padding-bottom: 72px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-ghost);
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .holocron-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .holocron-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 100;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-salmon);
  }

  .holocron-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-faint);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .holocron-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 100;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 26px);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-snow);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .holocron-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .holocron-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px 0;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .holocron-features li {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    width: 50%;
  }

  .holocron-features li::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--color-salmon);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .holocron-traction {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 44px;
  }

  .holocron-link {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-snow);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-faint);
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, gap 0.3s ease;
  }

  .holocron-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-salmon);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-salmon);
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .holocron-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-salmon);
    outline-offset: 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .eco-pipeline-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 100;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    color: var(--color-snow);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .eco-pipeline-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .eco-body { padding: 64px 24px 80px; }
    .holocron-features li { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
